gridguess - classroom board game
================================
gridguess is a classroom board game designed to be both easy to prepare and
fun. It functions on a grid of unknown questions displayed in columns with
point values. Each slot is defined by a formatted plaintext file.

Requirements
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup

Edit gg.c to configure the path to a font or name a font [font.ttf] in the
source directory. If you need to download a font, go to
[https://fonts.google.com].

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install gridguess (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install

